title: What We Love That Our Partners HATE + Can You Open An Airplane Door Mid-flight? + Easy TV Occupations Game
itunes:title: What We Love That Our Partners HATE + Can You Open An Airplane Door Mid-flight? + Easy TV Occupations Game
description:
Bobby and the crew share things that we love but our partners despise. Bobby read a story about a guy arrested for trying to open a door mid-flight on an airplane so he finds out if it’s actually possible. Bobby gives the crew a TV Character…and the have to name their job from their TV show.
